body:
How to add records in nisNetgroup Triple using Syntax IA5-String

Set-ADObject -Identity "OU=A,OU=B,OU=netgroup,OU=BLA,DC=BLA,DC=com" -Add @{'nisNetgroupTriple'="(,bla@domain.com,DOMAIN.COM)"} 

This is not working. How to correctly add a record ?

Easy to create :

New-ADObject -Name MYNAME -Type "nisNetgroup" -ProtectedFromAccidentalDeletion $Trueb -Path "OU=A,OU=B,OU=netgroup,OU=BLA,DC=BLA,DC=com" -OtherAttributes @{'nisNetgroupTriple'="(,bla@domain.com,DOMAIN.COM)"}
 
But the update of records is not documented.
